<h2 id="comments">Comments</h2>

<div id="c4761">

<p>There&#8217;s a third way. &#8220;The Country&#8221;. By living on 5 acres near signs reading &#8220;50 miles to next gas station&#8221; one gets yet another view.</p>

<p>So it&#8217;s not just urban/suburban.</p>

<p>Love.</p>

